text: I mean we have hisperic, evolist, bap, gait, dozens others. I sincerely believe some of these men will discover or create things worthy of being remembered. God knows no one else is. "Philosophy" communities are full of effeminate rail-thinkers, scientific forums with midwits ...

... of poetry. No one has any spark of originality, no one leaves the rails. Philosophy student who reads Mishima, then proceeds to read academic articles  about the books to try and understand them but HE CANNOT - what is wrong with him, where is his spirit? Political students..

know nothing about how the world works, they are foced to gulp down idiotic texts written by idiots. In London University the professors are literally the normies that 16 year old 4channers laugh about. Occultists are idiots who waste their lives in useless shit without gettin it

I rarely think about all the communities I've encountered irl and the Talebian disappointment I've felt to see how all of them are composed of absolute idiots. IDIOCY. This is the essence of it all. They look, they see - and yet the mind is blank there is no reaction in the brain

and this is seen here too. People pick a single thing and melt into it. Be it some bizarre horrifyingly idiotic politics, a brand, a theory that explains it all - the tumorous irony, the rotten arrogance, the smirks of idiocy - it all is a maddening and pulsating circle! Only...
yes :(

And yet we have to love everyone. If you feel smarter, anon, why are you not a shepherd to your brethren? - I talk to myself sleep-deprived - Why are you unable to save them, to set new rails for them to follow? Knowledge is useless by itself, it is dead, a burden.
